The evidence with the title 'How Zuckerberg's school reform for N.J. went awry ' says Sep 14, 2015  ... Five years ago this month , Mark Zuckerberg, Cory Booker, and Chris Christie announced on the Oprah Winfrey Show that the young founder of Facebook was pledging $ 100 million to transform the debilitated Newark school system into " a symbol of educational excellence for the whole nation . 
